Package: activAnalyzer.batch
Title: Parallel batch processing with ActiGraph .agd files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
     person('Pierre-Yves', 'de MÃ¼llenheim', email = 'pydemull@uco.fr', role = c('cre', 'aut'), 
     comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9157-7371"))
Description: The package allows the implementation of a framework to analyse several 
    ActiGraph .agd files in a row. Functions from the activAnalyzer R package are wrapped
    in a single function to analyse a given .agd file, and functions from the parabar R package
    are also wrapped in a single function to easily implement parallel processing for fast analysis.
